Read data

source("../step2/scripts/myRLib.R")
beta.ori <- read.table("output-run_step1/intermediate1__geno1_case__geno2_ctrl/ldpred-ori-beta.txt.gz", 
    header = T)
beta.ori$sid <- as.character(beta.ori$sid)
beta.ori <- beta.ori[order(beta.ori$sid), ]
files <- strsplit("output-run_step1/intermediate1__geno1_case__geno2_ctrl/ldpred_LDpred_p1.0000e+00.txt:output-run_step1/intermediate1__geno1_case__geno2_ctrl/ldpred_LDpred_p3.0000e-01.txt:output-run_step1/intermediate1__geno1_case__geno2_ctrl/ldpred_LDpred_p1.0000e-01.txt:output-run_step1/intermediate1__geno1_case__geno2_ctrl/ldpred_LDpred_p3.0000e-02.txt:output-run_step1/intermediate1__geno1_case__geno2_ctrl/ldpred_LDpred_p1.0000e-02.txt:output-run_step1/intermediate1__geno1_case__geno2_ctrl/ldpred_LDpred_p3.0000e-03.txt:output-run_step1/intermediate1__geno1_case__geno2_ctrl/ldpred_LDpred_p1.0000e-03.txt:output-run_step1/intermediate1__geno1_case__geno2_ctrl/ldpred_LDpred_p3.0000e-04.txt:output-run_step1/intermediate1__geno1_case__geno2_ctrl/ldpred_LDpred_p1.0000e-04.txt", 
    ":")[[1]]
ps <- strsplit("1,0.3,0.1,0.03,0.01,0.003,0.001,0.0003,0.0001", 
    ",")[[1]]

Plot

for (i in 1:length(ps)) {
    file.i <- files[i]
    p.i <- ps[i]
    cat("##", p.i, "
")
    cat("
")
    prs.i <- read.table(file.i, header = T)
    prs.i$sid <- as.character(prs.i$sid)
    prs.i <- prs.i[order(prs.i$sid), ]
    prs.i$log_odds <- correctAllele(prs.i$nt2, prs.i$nt1, beta.ori$a1, 
        beta.ori$log_odds)
    prs.i$ori_beta <- correctAllele(prs.i$nt2, prs.i$nt1, beta.ori$a1, 
        beta.ori$beta_ori)
    p1 <- ggplot(prs.i) + geom_histogram(aes(x = ori_beta, fill = "Original Beta"), 
        alpha = 0.3, bins = 100) + geom_histogram(aes(x = ldpred_beta, 
        fill = "LDpred Beta"), alpha = 0.3, bins = 100) + ggtitle("Histogram of Beta") + 
        xlab("Beta")
    df <- data.frame(x = prs.i$ori_beta, y = prs.i$ldpred_beta)
    p2 <- ggplot(data = prs.i, aes(x = ori_beta, y = ldpred_beta)) + 
        geom_point() + geom_smooth(method = "lm", se = FALSE, 
        color = "black", formula = y ~ 0 + x) + geom_text(x = quantile(df$x, 
        0.1), y = quantile(df$y, 0.99), label = lm_eqn_nointer(df), 
        parse = TRUE) + xlab("Original Beta") + ylab("LDpred Beta") + 
        ggtitle("Ldpred vs. Raw Beta")
    print(p1)
    print(p2)
    cat("
")
    cat("
")
}
